"title": "8431: fasting, reasons for",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8431",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture identifies a number of situations in which fasting is appropriate.</p>\n<h2>Situations in which fasting is appropriate</h2>\n<h3>Bereavement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr10:11-1Chr10:12\">1CH 10:11–10:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam31:11-1Sam31:13\">1SA 31:11–31:13</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:11-2Sam1:12\">2SA 1:11–1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:31-2Sam3:35\">2SA 3:31–3:35</a></p>\n<h3>Distress</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:3\">EST 4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:7\">1SA 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:34\">1SA 20:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:4-1Kgs21:6\">1KI 21:4–21:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:24\">PSA 109:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:18\">DAN 6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:33\">ACT 27:33</a></p>\n<h3>Penitence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:5-1Sam7:6\">1SA 7:5–7:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:1-Neh9:3\">NEH 9:1–9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:3-Dan9:6\">DAN 9:3–9:6</a> <em>Daniel identifies himself with the sin of the people</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:20\">DAN 9:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:13-Joel1:14\">JOL 1:13–1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:12-Joel2:15\">JOL 2:12–2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:5-Jonah3:9\">JON 3:5–3:9</a></p>\n<h3>Seeking God's intervention</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:15-2Sam12:17\">2SA 12:15–12:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:2-2Chr20:4\">2CH 20:2–20:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:21\">EZR 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:15-Esth4:16\">EST 4:15–4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:13-Ps35:14\">PSA 35:13–35:14</a></p>\n<h3>Seeking guidance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:26-Judg20:28\">JDG 20:26–20:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:9\">DEU 9:9</a> <em>Moses fasts before the revelation of the Law</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:1-Dan9:3\">DAN 9:1–9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:20-Dan9:23\">DAN 9:20–9:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:1-Dan10:2\">DAN 10:1–10:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:12\">DAN 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:1-Acts13:3\">ACT 13:1–13:3</a> <em>The church receives direction through the Holy Spirit while fasting.</em></p>\n<h3>Indicating earnestness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:12-Acts23:13\">ACT 23:12–23:13</a></p>",
